thread.title: Francis & Monique
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Francis & Monique

author: Francis & Monique
title: Francis & Monique
text: Jayson Watts, Kate Lilley and all the team at Nelson Alexander Flemington, provided us with quality and professional service and advice from the first time we met. The marketing strategy was executed perfectly culminating in a result far exceeding our expectations. Their communication during the whole campaign was first class and we would highly recommend them and wouldn't look anywhere else when entrusting someone with the sale of our property.
